<td bgcolor="#000099" valign="top" width="404">
<img src="assets/clear.gif" width="1" height="10" border="0"><br>
<span class="park11" id="parkwhite"><b>A New York boutique hotel that feels like a second home</b><br>
<img src="assets/clear.gif" width="1" height="7" border="0"><br>

A pleasant haven in the heart of Manhattan, the <b>70 park avenue hotel</b> is your 
personal 'pied-a-terre' - your home-away-from-home.<br>
<img src="assets/clear.gif" width="1" height="7" border="0"><br>

Passing through the <b>70 park avenue hotel</b>'s marble archway, guests immediately 
sense they've entered a luxurious and sophisticated urban refuge.  Our New 
York City boutique hotel features elegant d&#233;cor and state-of-the-art amenities.  
Guests will love details like the 42" flat screen televisions with Surround 
Sound, DVD/CD players in all the guestrooms and complimentary Wi-Fi Internet 
access available throughout the hotel.<br>
<img src="assets/clear.gif" width="1" height="7" border="0"><br>

Our four star level of service distinguishes this New York City boutique hotel. 
Enjoy services like the Mind, Body & Spa program with in-room yoga workouts 
or the indulgence of the fully-stocked gourmet honor bars. Guests are invited 
to our complimentary living room wine reception held nightly, a standard 
feature of Kimpton Hotels, to complete the feeling of a home-away-from home.<br>
<img src="assets/clear.gif" width="1" height="10" border="0"><br>
</span></td>
<td bgcolor="#000099" valign="top" width="20"><img src="assets/clear.gif" width="10" height="1" border="0"></td>

<td bgcolor="#000099" valign="top" width="370">
<img src="assets/clear.gif" width="1" height="10" border="0"><br>
<span class="park11" id="parkwhite">Just a handful of New York City hotels share the 
distinction of a Park Avenue address, and <b>70 park avenue hotel</b>'s Murray Hill setting 
has the added benefits of a friendly sense of community and lively history.   Grand 
Central Station is just four short blocks to the north along with prime office 
addresses. Fifth Avenue shopping, Union Square, Bryant Park, the United Nations, 
Rockefeller Center, Broadway, museums and nightlife are within walking distance.  
The hotel is convenient to downtown Manhattan as well.<br>
<img src="assets/clear.gif" width="1" height="7" border="0"><br>

Fresh from an extensive $19 million renovation under the direction of renowned 
residential designer Jeffrey Bilhuber, the <b>70 park avenue hotel</b> marks Kimpton Hotel's 
much-anticipated entry into the New York boutique hotel market.<br>
<img src="assets/clear.gif" width="1" height="7" border="0"><br>

Our motto is <b>Live Life Well</b>, and our guests experience the very best New York has to 
offer at what will come to feel like their own personal Park Avenue address.
</span><br>
<img src="assets/000099.gif" width="1" height="11" border="0"></td>
